# Research workspace — raw RE artifacts (APK, decompiled/extracted source,
# captures, JADX, logs, scripts). Everything here is local-only: never commit
# decompiled or proprietary source. Only README.md files are tracked, so new
# subdirectories (e.g. _extract/) are ignored by default.
research/**
!research/**/
!research/**/README.md
.claude/settings.local.json
